    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Empty query is used to warm up the connection, it resolves the DNS and init keep alive. Having a minLength can be useful in few cases but most of the time you can find your results before typing 3 chars. A mouseover event to trigger the empty query is probably a better approach.\n",
    "created_at": "2015-10-06T18:09:27Z",
