  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@Shipow Prefetching is a good idea but should be still configurable in my opinion. Starting at 1 character as a default is good enough but as a user, especially a mobile one, doesn't want an additional HTTP request fired with _no_ inserted terms.\n\n@vvo My use case is to replicate a documentation search box like [Laravel's](http://http://laravel.com/docs/5.1). As you can see no request are fired until at least one character is typed.\n",
