    "body": "> Just wondering if it was something we wanted out of the box without too much hassle. I was expecting .start() to behave more like an initializer, not actually searching without user's input / interaction.\n\nAlso wondering, there's #4. What we miss here is a good API Proposal to handle such things. Could be events (where you would then have to call .search) or API option on searchBox.\n",
